Group was founded in 2004 and the headquarter is in Melbourne, Australia. The registration number in Macau is **/2015.
We believe that we must continue to learn in order to maintain competitiveness and cope with the ever-changing work environment. Continuing education fund has become a social consensus.
Group has established offices in many countries and cities, cooperating with a lot of international colleges and professional institutions to provide a wide range of international quality education courses and professional certification examinations.
Group is authorized as the training center and test site by ANGLIA and as the training center by IELTS;
Group is authorized as the occupation competence certificate training center and test site by The Chinese Adult Education Association and Professional committer of the Enterprise Education which is permitted by the Ministry of Education of the People’s Republic of china; 
